snippet.title: Psycho Fear Teaser Gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Psycho Fear is a spine-chilling co-op survival-horror game where players must join forces to outwit, outlast, and escape from relentless horrors lurking in the shadows. 
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2208780/Psycho_Fear/
